# Conversation-viewer endpoint fixtures (Plan 2, §6.8).
#
# The committed per-scenario tree is ONLY:
#   <scenario>/input.env
#   <scenario>/golden-*.json
#
# The seeded SQLite DBs are rebuilt by bin/build-conversation-fixtures.py on
# every harness run (bin/cctally-conversation-test), so they are NOT committed —
# ignore the cache.db / stats.db + their WAL/SHM sidecars + any fake-HOME .local
# tree the harness clones into scratch. Keeps the working tree clean after a run.
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*/.local/
